<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ( bʿd bʿạdy wbʿd ʿnạdy bʿd mạ gẖryb wsẖryd
 jyt yạ ḥbyby mskt bạ̹ydy ạdyt lḥyạty ṭʿm jdyd )2
 ạlqrạr - ( mjdạaⁿ mjdạaⁿ lyk yạ fạdy sẖkrạaⁿ sẖkrạaⁿ ʿ ạlạ̉bdyẗ
 ḍmtny wftḥt ʿyny ʿly̱ ḥb mạlwsẖ ạ̉y ḥdwd )2
 2- ( fy kl ạ̉mạny wf ạ̉ʿmạly lạqyth jnby ạ̉ʿz ṣdyq
 ʿynh ʿly wạ̹ydh fy ạ̹ydy kẖṭwẗ bkẖṭwẗ fy kl ṭryq )2
 3- ( fy kl ạ̉hạty wf ṣʿwbạty lqyt ạlṣʿb mʿạh byhwn
 fy lḥẓẗ ṭlbth jạny bḥbh wạ̹dy̱ ḥyạty ṭʿm wlwn )2
 4- ( lmạ ạ̉fkr ạ̉w ạ̉tdẖkr ạ̉fḍạlk yạ ạ̹lhy ạlbạr
 ạ̉rfʿ ạ̹ydy wạjdd ʿhdy wạhtf lk wbkl fkẖạr )2</lyrics>
